<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blitz Tournament March 2026 - Queen's Chess Club</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vollkorn:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/tournament-page.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=League+Spartan:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="images/logo.jpg"/>
</head>

<%- include('header.ejs') %>

<body>
    <div class="tournament-hero" style="background-color: #e9e9e9;">
        <div class="tournament-hero-overlay">
            <div class="tournament-hero-content">
                <h1>Blitz Tournament</h1>
                <div class="tournament-date-badge">Sunday March 1st, 2026 · 1:00 PM</div>
                <p class="tournament-tagline">Fast-paced blitz · 9 rounds · 5+5 time control</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="centerer">
        <div class="tournament-container">
            <div class="tournament-info-panel">
                <div class="tournament-info-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                    <div class="tournament-info-content">
                        <h3>Location</h3>
                        <p>Stauffer 014<br>Queen's University, Kingston</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tournament-info-item">
                    <i class="far fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                    <div class="tournament-info-content">
                        <h3>Date & Time</h3>
                        <p>Sunday, March 1st, 2026<br>Start 1:00 PM</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tournament-info-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-chess-knight"></i>
                    <div class="tournament-info-content">
                        <h3>Format</h3>
                        <p>9 rounds · Time control: 5+5</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tournament-section">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>Looking for a fun weekend of fast-paced blitz games? Join us for our next blitz tournament on <strong>Sunday March 1st</strong> at Stauffer 014. Two sections, team prizes, and a great atmosphere—don't miss out!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="tournament-section">
                <h2>Sections & Prizes</h2>
                <div class="tournament-details-grid">
                    <div class="tournament-detail-card">
                        <h3>Individual Sections</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>U1500</strong> — $30 prize</li>
                            <li><strong>Open</strong> — $40 prize</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tournament-detail-card">
                        <h3>Team Prize (NEW)</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>$50</strong> team prize</li>
                            <li>Teams of 2 with average rating ≤ 1800 Elo</li>
                            <li>Team with the highest total points wins</li>
                            <li>Team sign-ups on-site only</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tournament-section">
                <h2>Registration & Pricing</h2>
                <div class="tournament-details-grid">
                    <div class="tournament-detail-card">
                        <h3>Entry Fees</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Queen's students: $10</li>
                            <li>Non-students: $15</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tournament-registration-cta">
                    <h2 class="registration-title">Register for the Blitz Tournament</h2>
                    <div class="registration-flex-container">
                        <div class="registration-button-container">
                            <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScwoVS8jnzVIGWv0lEtIbFhs-Dw2tYuAmiqPXsfYl09ewwxBA/viewform" target="_blank" class="tournament-register-button">Register Here</a>
                            <p class="tournament-registration-deadline">Sunday March 1st at 1pm · Stauffer 014</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="small-print">Registration form hosted on Google Forms.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="tournament-section tournament-contact-section">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>Questions? Reach out to the Queen's Chess Club:</p>
                <div class="tournament-contact-cards">
                    <div class="tournament-contact-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        <h3>Email</h3>
                        <p>queenschess@outlook.com</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tournament-contact-card">
                        <i class="fab fa-discord"></i>
                        <h3>Discord</h3>
                        <p>Join our server: <a href="https://discord.gg/queenschess">discord.gg/queenschess</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br><br>
    <%- include('footer.ejs'); %>

</body>
</html>
